'''Bothan Redrash''' was a disease that caused a severe outbreak of rashes all along the body. Bothan Redrash, not easily spread through physical contact, only affected [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]] and several other [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. [[Human/Legends|Humans]] could also be afflicted, since [[Wraith Squadron]] considered it as an agent to infect the [[Hawk-Bat (gunship)|''Hawkbat's'']] all-Human crew.

